eu_initiatives: We are currently working on the field of rule of law and justice, but our work is also closely linked to fundamental rights, gender equality and seeks to support international cooperation and development.
organisation_name: Regional Dialogue Institute for  organization of events and research  activity (RD)
subsection: Non-governmental organisations, platforms and networks and similar
relevant_communication: Human Rights Dialogue in Uzbekistan (Nov. 2010 - May 2012) under Call for Proposals EuropeAid/126352/C/ACT/Multi
goals__remit:
Regional Dialogue is an independent organization focused on promoting understanding between people and 
regions. Our work has thus far been specifically focused on Central Asia and aims to promote the exchange of 
knowledge, ideas and experience with the intention to foster understanding.
